data.description: Come check out this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath home that is ready to move in! Over 1500 sq ft with some new modern upgrades! Enjoy your privacy fenced back yard with a nice wood deck! The master has been tastefully decorated, boasts a tray ceiling, double vanity in the bathroom, and a walk in closet! The living room also has a tray ceiling, an open concept feel with the dining room, and a wood burning fireplace! Don't let this one slip by, come see it today!
